data.meta_description:
12 likes, 0 comments - dancinggrounds on January 6, 2023: "NEW LOCATION FOR TOMORROW -  now at NORDC Treme Center. Join us tomorrow for Afro-based workshop with long-time DG community member and teacher, Mariama Curry. This class, "The Untold Stories of My People," delves into the traditional dances of Africa and the preservation of histories that lives inside the movements. Class is $5!

See you at the Treme Center, 900 N Villere St, 10-11:30am. Register at link in bio or with our free mobile app.

#DancingGrounds #NolaDance #DgClasses #AfroBasedWorkshops #NORDC".
